<div>
  <div class="About center col-md-12">
    <h1 class="large">About Us:</h1>
    <p class="page-text">Bookhub was inspired by the idea of allowing students to buy and sell textbooks amongst eachother, without the hassle of bookstore lines, expensive prices, and horrible buy-back rates. With our simple to use dashboard, we aim to create a meeting point where students can come to sell textbooks at a reasonable rate and buy them at a better price than the University Bookstore.</p>
